- 'modest institutions': refers to small-sized universities;
- 'bloomed in the educational garden of 2022': refers to the performance metrics recorded in the year 2022;
- 'average overall scores': the averaged performance scores across various assessments for each university.

- "prolific professors" refers to faculty members with a high number of publications;
- "more than a decade's worth of publications" implies more than 10 publications;
- "volume of their scholarly output" refers to the count of publications.
